data.description: READY END OF AUGUST 2020! Virtual Tour of same floor plan here!https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=pA1WyuKL316&mls=1Excellent location! Located near shopping, military base, and schools. The Florence has a spacious front dining area, leading into the open kitchen. The kitchen has 42'' cabinets with granite countertops. Castle Ridge hardwood floors are in the dining/kitchen area. The laundry area is located on the second floor close to the bedrooms. The 3rd floor is a finished loft for a man cave, another bedroom, or whatever you choose! HOA includes lawn care, termite bond, 1x/yr pressure washing, 2x/yr pine straw and amenity center with pool.
